thread.title: BRIEF-Befimmo FY Net Profit Rises To 136.1 Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Befimmo FY Net Profit Rises To 136.1 Million Euros
text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - BEFIMMO SA:
* FY NET RENTAL INCOME EUR 142.4 MILLION VERSUS EUR 137.0 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY OPERATING PROFIT BEFORE RESULT ON PORTFOLIO EUR 117.0 MILLION VERSUS EUR 111.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY NET PROFIT EUR 136.1 MILLION VERSUS EUR 90.4 MILLION YEAR AGO
* DIVIDEND OUTLOOK OF €3.45 GROSS PER SHARE FOR THE 2018 FISCAL YEAR‍​
* OCCUPANCY RATE AT DEC 31 2017 ‍​94.44 PERCENT VERSUS 94.79 PERCENT YEAR AGO Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
